enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
section_title: Issues relating to registry systems under Protocol Article 7.4
sentences: Murray Ward introduced draft conclusions and a draft decision.
SBSTA adopted conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.29) and agreed to forward the draft decision on registry systems to the COP (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.29/Add.1).
